 non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip"},"ic_folder_categories.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/ic_folder_categories.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png"}}}